      "content": "but there is no \"present\" to focus on. it's just routine. eating, sleeping, working... like a machine. it's not like i'm living, i'm just functioning. the person who actually felt things, who had dreams and passion... that person is gone. i'm just the leftovers. the shell. and it's so heavy, carrying around a body that doesn't even feel like mine anymore.",
