      "content": "but that \"peace\" you're talking about... it feels more like nothingness. like being at the bottom of a well where none of the light reaches. if the real me is gone and all that's left is this empty shell that just goes through the motions... why does it have to keep going? why does this remnant even need to keep pretending?",
